@startuml svc-partner-integrations--post-partner-bookings-booking_id-confirm

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #2E86AB
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4F8
    LifeLineBorderColor #A23B72
    BoxBorderColor #F18F01
    BoxBackgroundColor #FFF8F0
    NoteBorderColor #c77b30
    NoteBackgroundColor #FEF3E7
}

header [[/microservices/svc-partner-integrations/#integration-context ⬆ svc-partner-integrations Integration Context]]

title POST /partner-bookings/{booking_id}/confirm\nConfirm a pending partner booking

participant "Client" as Client
participant "API Gateway" as GW #DBEAFE
participant "svc-partner-integrations" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-partner-integrations/]] #E8F4F8
participant "Reservations" as Res [[/microservices/svc-reservations/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Payments Svc" as Pay [[/microservices/svc-payments/]] #FFF8F0
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #FFF8F0
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #FCE4EC

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-partner-integrations.html#/Partner%20Bookings/confirmPartnerBooking View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /partner-bookings/{booking_id}/confirm
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Cross-Service Integration ==

Svc -> Res : [[/microservices/svc-reservations/#put-reservationsreservation_idstatus-transition-reservation-status Confirm reservation]]
activate Res #DBEAFE
Res --> Svc : OK
deactivate Res

Svc -> Pay : [[/microservices/svc-payments/#post-payments-process-a-payment Process commission]]
activate Pay #DBEAFE
Pay --> Svc : OK
deactivate Pay

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : SELECT parent WHERE id = ?
activate DB #FCE4EC
DB --> Svc : Parent row
deactivate DB
note right of DB : 404 if parent not found

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FCE4EC
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

== Async Events ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Send partner confirmation]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml